To: eqbards@onelist.com <eqbards@onelist.com>
Date: Wednesday, January 05, 2000 2:12 PM
Subject: Re: [eqbards] My Yk!!!


>> Bah taking it to personal. All I'm saying is that you said yourself vox
>> killled the raiders. I've seen dragosn done two ways, the dragon gets
>> spawked or the raiders get spanked doesn't seem to be a medium.
>
> Did I say that? My mistake... Oh wait, I just read all my sent mail.
> I never said that people died. Oops, your mistake. My guess is
> 90% of the people made it out alive. The people who were slain
> were the pet masters who were a little too careless. If we fought
> the dragon and lost, that one thing. I'm not ashamed to say we
> got spanked, but no one f'ing fought the dragon dude, heh. That's
> the point you seem to miss. Had the dominate server guild not
> stormed in and taken over, the 90% of the people alive would have
> regrouped and beat up Vox.
>
> Harmonic.
